<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Shipping Policy - CozySpot</title>
		<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

	</head>
	<body class="bg-black text-white font-['Inter'] antialiased">
		<!-- Navigation -->
		<div id="navigation-container"></div>

		<div id="ambient-bg">
			<div class="shooting-star"></div>
			<div class="shooting-star"></div>
			<div class="shooting-star"></div>
		</div>

		<div id="scroll-progress"></div>

		<!-- Main Content -->
		<main class="min-h-screen pt-24 pb-20">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10">
				<!-- Header -->
				<div class="mb-12">
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase italic mb-4">Shipping Policy</h1>
					<p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Last updated: January 17, 2026</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Quick Summary -->
				<div class="mb-12 p-6 bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-xl">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-400 mb-3">Shipping Overview</h2>
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-white/80">
						<div>
							<p class="text-sm text-white/50 mb-1">Processing Time</p>
							<p class="font-semibold">1-3 business days</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<p class="text-sm text-white/50 mb-1">Delivery Time</p>
							<p class="font-semibold">3-14 business days</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<p class="text-sm text-white/50 mb-1">Free Shipping</p>
							<p class="font-semibold">Is already factored into the price</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<p class="text-sm text-white/50 mb-1">Shipping Regions</p>
							<p class="font-semibold">USA, EU, UK, Canada</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Content -->
				<div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-white/70">
					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Processing Time</h2>
						<p>All orders are processed within <strong>1-3 business days</strong> (excluding weekends and holidays) after receiving your order confirmation.</p>
						<p class="mt-2">You will receive a shipping confirmation email with a tracking number once your order has been shipped.</p>

						<div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500/20 rounded-lg">
							<p class="text-yellow-400"><strong>Note:</strong> During peak seasons (Black Friday, Christmas, etc.), processing times may be extended by 1-2 days.</p>
						</div>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Shipping Rates & Delivery Times</h2>

						<div class="overflow-x-auto">
							<table class="w-full mt-4 border-collapse">
								<thead>
									<tr class="border-b border-white/10">
										<th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-white font-semibold">Region</th>
										<th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-white font-semibold">Delivery Time</th>
										<th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-white font-semibold">Standard Rate</th>
										<th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-white font-semibold">Free Shipping</th>
									</tr>
								</thead>
								<tbody>
									<tr class="border-b border-white/5">
										<td class="py-3 px-4">United States</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4"><span class="text-green-400">2-5 business days</span></td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">$4.99</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4 text-green-400">Orders $50+</td>
									</tr>
									<tr class="border-b border-white/5">
										<td class="py-3 px-4">European Union</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">7-12 business days</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">$6.99</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4 text-green-400">Orders $50+</td>
									</tr>
									<tr class="border-b border-white/5">
										<td class="py-3 px-4">United Kingdom</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">7-12 business days</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">$6.99</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4 text-green-400">Orders $50+</td>
									</tr>
									<tr class="border-b border-white/5">
										<td class="py-3 px-4">Canada</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">10-15 business days</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">$5.99</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4 text-green-400">Orders $50+</td>
									</tr>
									<tr class="border-b border-white/5">
										<td class="py-3 px-4">Australia</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">10-15 business days</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">$7.99</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4 text-green-400">Orders $75+</td>
									</tr>
									<tr>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">Rest of World</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">10-15+ business days</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4">$9.99</td>
										<td class="py-3 px-4 text-green-400">Orders $100+</td>
									</tr>
								</tbody>
							</table>
						</div>

						<p class="mt-4 text-sm">*Delivery times are estimates and may vary due to customs processing, carrier delays, or unforeseen circumstances.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. Order Tracking</h2>
						<p>Once your order ships, you will receive a confirmation email containing:</p>
						<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>Tracking number</li>
							<li>Link to track your package</li>
							<li>Estimated delivery date</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="mt-4">Please allow 2-5 days for tracking information to update after receiving your shipping confirmation.</p>

						<div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
							<p class="text-white/90"><strong>Tip:</strong> If tracking hasn't updated in 7+ days, please contact us. We'll investigate and help resolve the issue.</p>
						</div>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">4. Customs, Duties & Taxes</h2>
						<p>For international orders outside the United States:</p>
						<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>Your order may be subject to import duties and taxes</li>
							<li>These charges are the responsibility of the recipient</li>
							<li>We have no control over these charges and cannot predict their amount</li>
							<li>Contact your local customs office for more information</li>
						</ul>

						<div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">For EU Customers:</h4>
							<p>Orders under â‚¬150 may have VAT included at checkout (where applicable). For orders above this threshold, you may need to pay additional import duties upon delivery.</p>
						</div>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">5. Shipping Restrictions</h2>
						<p>We currently do not ship to:</p>
						<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>P.O. Boxes (for some products)</li>
							<li>Military addresses (APO/FPO)</li>
							<li>Countries under trade sanctions</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="mt-4">If your country is not listed in our shipping options at checkout, we are unable to deliver to your location at this time.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">6. Delivery Issues</h2>

						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-2">Package Not Received</h3>
						<p>If your package has not arrived within the estimated delivery timeframe:</p>
						<ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>Check your tracking information for updates</li>
							<li>Verify your shipping address was entered correctly</li>
							<li>Check with neighbors or your local post office</li>
							<li>Contact us if the package shows "delivered" but you haven't received it</li>
						</ol>

						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-2">Lost Packages</h3>
						<p>If your package is lost in transit, please contact us. We will work with the carrier to locate your package or arrange a replacement/refund.</p>

						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-2">Damaged Packages</h3>
						<p>If your package arrives damaged, please:</p>
						<ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>Take photos of the damaged packaging and contents</li>
							<li>Contact us within 24 hours of delivery</li>
							<li>We will arrange a replacement or refund</li>
						</ol>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">7. Address Changes</h2>
						<p>If you need to change your shipping address after placing an order:</p>
						<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>Contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:cozyspot.team@gmail.com" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">cozyspot.team@gmail.com</a></li>
							<li>Include your order number and the correct address</li>
							<li>Address changes can only be made before the order ships</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="mt-4 text-yellow-400/80"><strong>Note:</strong> We are not responsible for packages delivered to incorrect addresses provided by the customer.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">8. Multiple Items</h2>
						<p>If you order multiple items, they may be shipped separately and arrive at different times. You will receive separate tracking information for each shipment.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">9. Contact Us</h2>
						<p>For any shipping-related questions or concerns:</p>
						<div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
							<p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:cozyspot.team@gmail.com" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">cozyspot.team@gmail.com</a></p>
							<p class="mt-2"><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 24 hours</p>
							<p class="mt-2"><strong>Subject Line:</strong> Include "Shipping Inquiry - [Order Number]"</p>
						</div>
					</section>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>

		<!-- Footer -->
		<div id="footer-container"></div>

		<script src="script.js"></script>
		<script>
			fetch('navigation.html')
				.then(res => res.text())
				.then(html => {
					document.getElementById('navigation-container').innerHTML = html
					if (typeof runMenuScripts === 'function') runMenuScripts()
				})

			fetch('footer.html')
				.then(res => res.text())
				.then(html => {
					document.getElementById('footer-container').innerHTML = html
				})
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
